name: When the devil comes around
description:
I killed it once before
It’s a strange thing trying to ignore
That silent sound
When the Devil comes…
he’s just outside the door
So familiar
Always wanting more
And I can’t slow down...
When the Devil comes around…
Who’s gonna save me now?
If I’ve already turned the lights out on us?
A man just needs a friend
Not a stranger who only just pretends
To let him out
when the Devil comes around

VR animation.
